highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Moscow Mule” is the highest at #2.
“Te Felicito” by Shakira and Rauw Alejandro is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 81 spots at #91.
“Moscow Mule” by Bad Bunny is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 275 weeks straight.
